Package: simulationcraft-common
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Common files for SimulationCraft, a combat simulator for WoW (TM).
 This package contains files that can be used from either the command line
 or the graphical user interface of SimulationCraft, such as raid profiles.

